    <item>
      <title>印度财政部长预计人均收入将几乎翻一番</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/india-s-finance-minister-sees-per-capita-income-almost-doubling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度财政部长尼尔玛拉·西塔拉曼表示，随着经济持续增长，五年内人均收入将几乎翻一番，同时警告称，目前的全球环境比过去更加严峻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/india-s-finance-minister-sees-per-capita-income-almost-doubling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:15:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>即使禁令解除，土耳其仍将保留部分小麦进口限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/turkey-to-keep-some-curbs-on-wheat-imports-even-when-ban-lifts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的一份文件显示，土耳其计划在本月四个月的小麦进口禁令结束后继续限制部分小麦进口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/turkey-to-keep-some-curbs-on-wheat-imports-even-when-ban-lifts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:11:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
